        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(activity): scope activity cancellation by item",
        "body": "## Summary\n- Scope `github-activity` workflow cancellation by repo, event/action, and item/comment/review/workflow identity instead of one repo-wide `activity` group.\n- Preserve workflow-run observer coalescing under the existing repo-level `workflow-run` key.\n- Update the workflow assertion so unrelated issue/PR activity cannot cancel each other before dispatch.\n\nFixes #311\n\n## Verification\n- `pnpm install --frozen-lockfile`\n- `pnpm run build:all`\n- `node --test --test-name-pattern \"github activity workflow scopes cancellation\" test\\clawsweeper.test.ts`\n- `pnpm run check:active-surface`\n- `pnpm run check:limits`\n- `pnpm run lint:scripts`\n- `pnpm exec oxfmt --check .github\\workflows\\github-activity.yml test\\clawsweeper.test.ts`\n- `git diff --check` (CRLF warning only)\n- `codex -c service_tier=fast review --uncommitted` reported no actionable regressions.\r\n",
